<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I try to create a dbtable using zf (command: zf create dbtable )
I get an Exception with the following message
bq. <em>A models directory was not found</em></p>

<p>Line 63 in Zend\Tool\Project\Provider\DbTable reads
bq. <em>if (!($modelsDirectory instanceof ProjectProfile\Resource)) {</em></p>

<p>I guess it should be
bq. <em>if (!($modelsDirectory instanceof \Zend\Tool\Project\Profile\Resource\Resource)) {</em></p>

    </div>
